</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ujzonn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jzonn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Have posted before</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/00 7:26:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://personal.bhm.bellsouth.net/bhm/r/p/rpo2/Jzonn_Icon.png WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Conesus--- FFA planes or schedule</span><hr size=1> Oops.  Wasn't trying to advocate that system, just provide a different viewpoint to systems as opposed to the SolRo one.  I don't feel GH dominated the KGC, but I don't think it was the be-all, end-all of systems either.  I don't think it was 'fair' to those who couldn't be on the board at the right time and I feel it could be manipulated (again due to some timing issues). <p><B><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#004080">Jzonn Stormwolf &lt;Unguilded&gt;</B></FONT><BR>
<I><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#ffffff">Ranger of Karana</I></FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Zerin</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/00 7:34:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:</span><hr size=1> Holy crap, people still do planes for anything other then the gods still? At least on CT it wasn't too common to see people in there on days that the gods weren't up. And if there was it was always plenty big to share. Plane scheduling sucks and I think people shouldn't be so quick to jump on them when we have NO idea how the situation is like yet. Just my opinion...<br>
